22 amount of the refund to which he is entitled shall be donated to the Grambling
23 University National Alumni Association in lieu of that amount being paid to him as
24 a refund. The refund shall be reduced by the amount so designated. The designation
25 shall be made at the time of the filing of the current year tax return and shall be made
26 upon the income tax return form as prescribed by the secretary of the Department of
